properrtyDescription: This stunning 4BHK villa offers breathtaking ocean views and a luxurious living experience in one of Miami’s most sought-after locations. The property boasts a contemporary design with an open floor plan that seamlessly connects indoor and outdoor spaces. The spacious living room is complemented by floor-to-ceiling windows, allowing natural light to flood the interiors. The modern kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, custom cabinetry, and a sleek breakfast island. Each of the four bedrooms is elegantly designed, featuring en-suite bathrooms, walk-in closets, and private balconies. The master suite includes a spa-inspired bathroom with a jacuzzi, rain shower, and double vanity. Outside, the property features a beautifully landscaped garden, a large infinity swimming pool, and a sun deck perfect for relaxation and entertaining. Additional amenities include a smart home system, CCTV security, and a gated entrance for maximum privacy and safety. The villa is conveniently located near top-rated schools, shopping centers, and fine dining establishments. Whether you're looking for a dream home or an investment opportunity, this property offers everything you need for an unparalleled lifestyle.
